{"tid":1004932,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣都好掛住97-08年既電視?","createTime":"2019-02-01T23:29:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-02T14:29:44.000Z","uid":17510,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d10ecf95ad78816b7552b9498dc161b211362ff1","tid":1004932,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T23:29:05.000Z","msg":"依段期間既TVB講得上係全盛時期<br />\n好多劇集同主題曲都係經典<br />\n<br />\n可惜而家為左奶共而唔再拍自己劇集<br />\n又唔再捧新人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳志雲當年都算係捧紅左5個靚仔同好多好多女星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家TVB簡直係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23cb383e29da5d2461f24c81d875154c9ce22622","tid":1004932,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T23:29:38.000Z","msg":"有咩劇？"},{"pid":"ae70a6ebf521f74fed074cb470ebc4207c10d995","tid":1004932,"uid":166670,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23cb383e29da5d2461f24c81d875154c9ce22622","tid":1004932,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T23:29:38.000Z","msg":"有咩劇？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T23:35:26.000Z","msg":"與神同行"},{"pid":"5889ca74dde09b05dd6830b5a97a1e86549e69ad","tid":1004932,"uid":161014,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T23:36:51.000Z","msg":"糖心風暴 (第1  2集)  已經係最好例子"},{"pid":"e91b6ea3e01ec19ffa55e6eedcfaab0708c09dae","tid":1004932,"uid":17510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"23cb383e29da5d2461f24c81d875154c9ce22622","tid":1004932,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTim