車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入面除左馬德鐘 D新人其實都係有好大進步空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3930683e94c6917236e40d87eea09561a173a43f","tid":1004932,"uid":17510,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"9fd436a50e5210a442d87072fef53907d5e35e3b","tid":1004932,"uid":124292,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e91b6ea3e01ec19ffa55e6eedcfaab0708c09dae","tid":1004932,"uid":17510,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"23cb383e29da5d2461f24c81d875154c9ce22622","tid":1004932,"uid":43924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T23:29:38.000Z","msg":"有咩劇？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T23:42:48.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆  好多人都拎當年既劇集黎同美劇比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過我就覺得TVB果陣香港味道其實唔係咁差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T23:45:21.000Z","msg":"食開屎係唔同啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T00:02:15.000Z","msg":"無錯係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好自豪係食屎大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美劇成個國家咁多觀眾  對比起香港市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真心唔明啲踩港劇既人點樣可以覺得要TVB去好似外國咁去用咁巨額既投資<br />\n係依個基礎上已經唔再係一個公平比較<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於對比起啲乜乜傳物物傳<br />\n我係絕對認為TVB更勝一籌<br />\n即使用最近既翻生武林黎比較都唔會輸蝕果啲XX傳"},{"pid":"9a68a91f1939fcc49c705b9f56eeb5e7bd0d30d7","tid":1004932,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8712b5276c1651525fca1895f1d276fd5e45aa54","tid":1004932,"uid":52524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T00:01:31.000Z","msg":"以前D演員同而家都爭幾班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似你講個堆咁 江華 宣萱 關詠荷 歐陽震華 都係好戲之人<br />\n<br />\n而家近年TVB上到位都係得套白車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入面除左馬德鐘 D新人其實都係有好大進步空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T00:07:31.000Z","msg":"青黃不接係好大問題<br />\n<br />\n其實真係唔知係怪時勢定係怪TVB管理層太廢<br />\n<br />\n時勢上  支國崛起係事實<br />\n班演員稍為紅一啲就即刻去左支國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n10年之前其實都尚算無走得咁誇張<br />\n之後果啲真係明明覺得佢做得幾好   點解唔見左人?!<br />\n一google先知原來走左去大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過同時間其實都真係有好多投訴CCTVB管理心法好有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有生之年如果可以再次見到香港有返一個自己既電視台就好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e2d64efa0106468389cc3f4d1289183a52dd24f","tid":1004932,"uid":52524,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9a68a91f1939fcc49c705b9f56eeb5e7bd0d30d7","tid":1004932,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8712b5276c1651525fca1895f1d276fd5e45aa54","tid":1004932,"uid":52524,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T00:01:31.000Z","msg":"以前D演員同而家都爭幾班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似你講個堆咁 江華 宣萱 關詠荷 歐陽震華 都係好戲之人<br />\n<br />\n而家近年TVB上到位都係得套白車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n入面除左馬德鐘 D新人其實都係有好大進步空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-02T00:07:31.000Z","msg":"青黃不接係好大問題<br />\n<br />\n其實真係唔知係怪時勢定係怪TVB管理層太廢<br />\n<br />\n時勢上  支國崛起係事實<br />\n班演員稍為紅一啲就即刻去左支國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n10年之前其實都尚算無走得咁誇張<br />\n之後果啲真係明明覺得佢做得幾好   點解唔見左人?!<br />\n一google先知原來走左去